\end{equation}\)</li>
  <li><strong>Positive patch loss</strong>:
\(\begin{equation}
L_{p o s}\left(F, F^{t}\right)=\frac{1}{N} \sum_{(x, y) \in P_{p o s}}\left\|F_{x, y}^{t}-F_{x, y}\right\|_{1}
\end{equation}\)</li>
</ol>

